<Layout>
	<main>
		<div class="top">
			<div class="top-left">
				<h1 class="top-title">團隊成員</h1>
				<p class="top-text">
					SITCON 年會每年皆是許多志工奉獻時間與精神所舉辦，沒有大家的付出，就不可能會有如此內容豐富且高品質的年會，希望大家在參加之餘，也不要忘記背後工作人員的付出。若你對參與 SITCON
					年會的籌備有興趣，歡迎填寫跳坑表單或是關注 SITCON 的郵件論壇，明年的籌備開始時，你就會收到相關的資訊！
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="top-right">
				<div class="top-right-btn-group">
					<button class="top-right-btn">跳坑表單</button>
					<button class="top-right-btn">郵件論壇</button>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		{team_data.map(team => <Team member={team.member} name={team.name} description={team.description} />)}
	</main>
	<MemberInfo />
	<Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
	main {
		min-height: 100vh;
		padding: 5rem 4rem;
	}

	@media (max-width: 48rem) {
		main {
			padding: 5rem 3rem;
		}
	}

	.top {
		padding: 5.5rem 0;
		display: flex;
		justify-content: space-between;
	}

	@media (max-width: 48rem) {
		.top {
			flex-direction: column;
			gap: 2rem;
		}
	}
	.top-title {
		font-size: 4rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
	}

	.top-text {
		font-size: 1rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		font-family: "GenKiGothic2 TW";
		word-break: break-word;
		max-width: 34rem;
	}

	.top-right {
		align-content: end;
	}

	.top-right-btn-group {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: row;
		gap: 1rem;
	}

	@media (max-width: 48rem) {
		.top-right-btn-group {
			flex-direction: column;
		}
	}

	.top-right-btn:hover {
		background-color: #ffdc8a;
		transform: translateY(0.25rem);
		box-shadow: 0 0.25rem 0.5rem rgba(255, 209, 114, 0.3);
	}

	.top-right-btn {
		background-color: #e8bb5f;
		color: #2b2e3a;
		padding: 1rem 2rem;
		border-radius: 62rem;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		font-weight: bold;
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
		box-shadow: 0 0.25rem 0.5rem rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
		text-align: center;
		cursor: pointer;
	}
</style>
